{{Politics of Tajikistan}}
'''2013年塔吉克斯坦总统选举'''于2013年11月6日举行<ref>{{Cite news|title=Volatile Tajikistan sets presidential election for November 6|url=http://news.yahoo.com/volatile-tajikistan-sets-presidential-election-november-6-085620488.html|agency=Reuters|date=2013-08-30|accessdate=2013-11-07|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906191440/https://news.yahoo.com/volatile-tajikistan-sets-presidential-election-november-6-085620488.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[塔吉克斯坦|塔吉克斯坦]]独立后的第四次总统选举。此次选举共有在任总统[[埃莫马利·拉赫蒙|埃莫马利·拉赫蒙]]等六位候选人，获胜者将赢得七年总统任期。<ref name=hqsb/> 评论普遍认为在任总统[[埃莫马利·拉赫蒙|埃莫马利·拉赫蒙]]的对手缺乏竞争力<ref name=AJ>{{Cite news|title=Tajikistan holds presidential election|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/11/tajikistan-holds-presidential-election-201311652838364800.html|agency=Al Jazeera|date=2013-11-06|accessdate=2013-11-07|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930101306/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/11/tajikistan-holds-presidential-election-201311652838364800.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拉赫蒙将轻松连任。反对党[[伊斯兰复兴党|伊斯兰复兴党]]与[[社会民主党_(塔吉克斯坦)|社会民主党]]推荐[[奥伊尼霍尔·博博纳扎罗娃|奥伊尼霍尔·博博纳扎罗娃]]参选，但因收集的选民签名不足，未能成功注册。伊斯兰复兴党和社会民主党呼吁选民抵制选举。<ref name=aljaz>{{cite news|title=Tajikistan holds presidential election|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/11/tajikistan-holds-presidential-election-201311652838364800.html|agency=Al Jazeera|date=2013-11-06|accessdate=2013-11-07|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930101306/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/11/tajikistan-holds-presidential-election-201311652838364800.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2013年11月7日，塔吉克斯坦中央选举公投委员会主席绍西勇在塔吉克斯坦首都[[杜尚别|杜尚别]]宣布了初步计票结果，埃莫马利·拉赫蒙得票83.6%，成功连任<ref name=xhw/>。最终结果将在投票结束后十日内公布。

== 候选人 ==
此次总统大选共有6位成功注册的候选人。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title = Tajik Opposition Candidate Bows Out Of Race|date = 2013-10-11|url = http://www.rferl.org/content/tajik-opposition-president/25133663.html|agency = RFE/RL's Tajik Service|accessdate = 2013-11-07|archive-date = 2016-09-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160918152631/http://www.rferl.org/content/tajik-opposition-president/25133663.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 候选人必须收集210,000个选民签名（5 %的选民签名）才能成功注册。<ref>{{Cite news|title = Presidential candidate must collect 210 thousand signatures|date = 2013-09-02|agency = Asia Plus|url = http://news.tj/en/news/presidential-candidate-must-collect-210-thousand-signatures|access-date = 2013-11-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141011141603/http://news.tj/en/news/presidential-candidate-must-collect-210-thousand-signatures|archive-date = 2014-10-11|dead-url = yes}}</ref> 塔吉克斯坦最大的反对党[[伊斯兰复兴党|伊斯兰复兴党]]与另一反对党[[社会民主党_(塔吉克斯坦)|社会民主党]]组成“支持改革”竞选联盟，推荐[[奥伊尼霍尔·博博纳扎罗娃|奥伊尼霍尔·博博纳扎罗娃]]参选<ref>{{Cite news|title = Zayirov Calls on His Supporters to Rally around Aynihal Babanazarova|date = 2013-09-12|url = http://news.tj/en/news/zayirov-calls-his-supporters-rally-around-aynihal-babanazarova|agency = Asia-Plus|access-date = 2013-11-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131018040215/http://news.tj/en/news/zayirov-calls-his-supporters-rally-around-aynihal-babanazarova|archive-date = 2013-10-18|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，但因只收集到了202,000个签名，不足210,000个，只好退出大选。伊斯兰复兴党表示，他们征集签名时遭到地方政府骚扰，导致无法达到5%的门槛。伊斯兰复兴党和社会民主党呼吁选民抵制选举，并称这次选举只是一出大戏而已。<ref name=aljaz/>

